Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:16.89,Title,,0,0,0,,Icebound Ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.02,end,,0,0,0,,To be continued
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,wolves and goats were always at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After generations and generations of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the relationship between the wolves and goats finally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy and Weslie’s handshake is the symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of a new era of peace between wolves and goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the path to peace is not as simple as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no “scientific expedition team” here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, a blizzard just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry back onto the Magic Trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you might as well just roll over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck was the one who decided to come to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going with all of this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A scientific expedition team has discovered some ruins at the Ice Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re inviting me to investigate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be a very cold place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the Ice Pole used to be an ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned into an icy, snowy place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,after it froze during the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we please come with you, Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way, you can practice writing travelogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, none of us will have time for writing travelogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, little goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d actually like for you guys to call me Uncle Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Weslie and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to the Ice Pole for a scientific expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the Ice Pole during such hot weather must be so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky and Weslie have been shoveling snow for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re done shoveling at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re about to freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside and get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How could there possibly be anyone out in such a blizzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the Magic Trains to maximum power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We might just be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Trains, full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are we supposed to find the expedition team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just snow, snow, and more snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren’t even any signs around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the expedition team is right up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you guys think
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that this sign is very suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve come all the way here, so we should at least check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I already see the expedition team’s campsite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go check it out, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this place completely deserted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This puppet looks just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m coming to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, this is how I drove Sirius
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat the evil Black Cloud,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,saving Weslie, his friends, and the Flying Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy’s amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When are we going on another adventure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Adventure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t you like having Daddy to play with you every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy and the others sent an SOS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to rescue Weslie and the others right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We fell from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already sent an SOS to Goats’ Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s press on for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and see if there’s another way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy, why does it feel like we keep descending?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the legendary pre-Ice Age undersea capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the legend is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend has it that long before land animals emerged,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a civilized city under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Within it was unexplained, mysterious technology
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that was well before its time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the sea froze over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Archaeologists speculate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was a phenomenon caused by the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the city has been sealed in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there’s something at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Translation missing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from this pillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it really is completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it useful in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This was made for the purpose of allowing elderly people to better read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it just a thing for telling time, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go. I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a big clock dial can’t be just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it can even let us time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, travelers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If he’s not captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he’ll bring harm to Goats’ Village again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it’s nothing more than a fast-running train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,full speed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ice Pole is massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a flare, where in the world am I supposed to search?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with the sudden earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, guys, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be on my way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This flare is a little too strong, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst part of adventuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is… Is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a dinosaur?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
